Usage: get_constraint_mode [-help] <modeName> {-sdc_files  | -ilm_sdc_files  | -tcl_vars }

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<modeName>            # Name of the constraint mode to query (string, required)
-ilm_sdc_files        # Returns the ILM flow SDC files associated with the
                      # specified constraint mode (bool, optional)
-sdc_files            # Returns SDC files associated with the specified
                      # constraint mode (bool, optional)
-tcl_vars             # Returns the list of tcl vars associated with the
                      # specified constraint mode (bool, optional)